## 字体规范（MEXC Sans 优先）

```css
body {
  font-family: var(--font-family-base);
  font-size: 14px;
  line-height: 20px;
  color: var(--color-text-primary);
  background: var(--color-bg-page);
  -webkit-font-smoothing: antialiased;
}

/* 价格、数字、百分比 — 必须用等宽字体 */
.price, .number, [data-type="price"] {
  font-family: var(--font-family-mono);
  font-variant-numeric: tabular-nums;
  font-feature-settings: "tnum";
}
```

### Typography Scale（直接对应 Figma 组件名）
| Figma 名称 | 字号/行高 | 字重 | CSS 变量 |
|-----------|----------|------|---------|
| Display/L-56 Bold | 56px / 64px | 700 | `--text-display-56` |
| Display/1-36 Bold | 36px / 44px | 700 | `--text-display-36` |
| Headline/M-32 Bold | 32px / 40px | 700 | `--text-headline-32` |
| Title/0-24 Bold | 24px / 32px | 700 | `--text-title-24` |
| Title/1-20 Bold | 20px / 28px | 700 | `--text-title-20` |
| Title/0-18 Bold | 18px / 26px | 600 | `--text-title-18` |
| Title/2-16 Bold | 16px / 24px | 700 | `--text-title-16` |
| Body/XL-20 Regular | 20px / 28px | 400 | `--text-body-20` |
| Body/1-16 Medium | 16px / 24px | 500 | `--text-body-16` |
| Body/M-14 Medium | 14px / 20px | 500 | `--text-body-14-med` |
| Body/M-14 Regular | 14px / 20px | 400 | `--text-body-14` |
| Body/S-12 Regular | 12px / 16px | 400 | `--text-body-12` |

